        <updateDate>2021-11-30T19:58:17Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong></strong>This resolution expresses the sense of the House of Representatives that the United States must establish (1) electricity as a basic human right; and (2) a publicly- and community-owned power system that is just, equitable, antiracist, and resilient to climate changes and disasters.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Expressing that the United States must establish electricity as a basic human right and public good, and eradicate the reliance on monopolized, profit-driven utility corporations and providers and the flawed regulatory regime that has failed to regulate these utilities in the public interest.</title>
